Business Performance Dashboard

Power BI | Data Visualization | Business Intelligence

Project Overview

This comprehensive Power BI dashboard was developed for a retail chain with 15 locations across Multan. The dashboard integrates sales data, inventory levels, and customer behavior metrics to provide actionable insights for business decision-making.

The solution includes real-time tracking of key performance indicators (KPIs), customer segmentation analysis, and sales forecasting capabilities. By implementing this dashboard, the client was able to identify underperforming product categories and optimize their inventory management.

Key Achievements

  • Reduced inventory costs by 22% through optimized stock management
  • Identified high-value customer segments leading to 15% increase in repeat business
  • Automated reporting saving 20+ hours per week in manual reporting
  • Implemented real-time sales tracking across all locations

Technology Stack

Power BI DAX SQL Server Power Query Azure Excel
